		<td><b>WiiU e shop officially closed for agreements with devs</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For NOA and NOE regions, the window for applying for software releases on the Wii U e shop closed Dec 22nd, and will close in Japan on the 29th. Support for devs will remain in service in early 2018, but no new applications will be handled.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


